# Great News from the legislative process: 

The European Parliament Committee on Legal Affairs published amendment 51 …
It adds a requirement for #interoperability in **core** platform services

The piece reads

&gt;(f)  –  allow business users, **end users**, providers of ancillary services **and other providers of core platform services** access to and interoperability with the same operating system, hardware or software features that are available or used in the provision by the gatekeeper of any ancillary services **and core platform services;**

